<h2 class="bold font-l">Toradora!</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Taiga's father never shows up to his daughter's performance. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DaddyDidntShow" class='trope-example-link'>Daddy Didn't Show</a></p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
